detail.name: Frieza

[Barrier] (This card can’t be chosen by the skills of your opponent's cards.)
[When Attacking](2) : Choose up to 1 Rest Mode Battle Card with a cost of 5 or less in your opponent's Battle Area and place it into its owner's Drop.

faq.question: You choose your opponent's Rest Mode FB03-009 <Jiren> for this card's [When Attacking] skill. FB03-009 <Jiren> has a [Permanent] skill that prevents it from being KO'd once per turn, but is it placed into its owner's Drop?
faq.answer: Yes, it's placed into its owner's Drop.

faq.question: このカードの【アタック時】で相手のレストの「FB03-009　ジレン」を選びました。1ターンに1回KOされない【永続】スキルは有効ですが、「FB03-009　ジレン」はドロップに置かれますか？
faq.answer: はい、ドロップに置かれます。
